This project includes a placeholder app/google-services.json only so GitHub Actions can build the APK immediately.

For real push notifications:
1. Go to Firebase Console.
2. Create a Firebase project.
3. Add Android app with package name: com.arewascope.app
4. Download the real google-services.json.
5. Replace app/google-services.json with the real file.
6. Commit the change and rebuild the APK.
